 Demo application screenshots for this article  By design instead of mapping java types to SQLite supported SQL datatypes KittyORM maps them directly into SQLite affinities, KittyORM supports predefined mapping for primitive java types, primitive wrappers, byte array, enumerations and following types: java.lang.String, java.util.Date, java.util.Currency, java.util.Calendar, java.sql.Timestamp, java.math.BigInteger, java.math.BigDecimal, java.io.File, android.net.Uri.
